description: A French doctor says tests on samples from patients show the virus was present last year.
title: Coronavirus: New lows for deaths in France, Spain and Italy
title_page: Coronavirus: New lows for deaths in France, Spain and Italy - BBC News
maintext: France is planning to lift its lockdown on 11 May, when children will return to school in phases, some businesses will reopen and people will be able to travel within 100km (60 miles) of their homes without the need for a document giving a reason for their movement.
